title: New Creator: AvaGG
body:
[Name] 
AvaGG

[Socials]
https://twitter.com/AvaGG
https://www.twitch.tv/avagg
https://www.instagram.com/ava.gg/

[Info] 
Ava is an OG streamer that likes beer and videogames. Ava is known for her deep love of The Last Of Us, her undying passion for FPS games, and for being the fierce leader of the Avaholics. Ava is excited to build her digital economy with Rally! 

[Usecases]
Launch - Ava will be rewarding her mods and subscribers with giftcoins.
Holding - Ava will use the Discord bot for a private channel, and post funny memes *ONLY* in that channel.
Transaction - Ava will do a weekly 'KarAVAoke' night where her fans can use $AVA coins to do song requests.

[Treasury Grant Tier]
$1000

A 'yes' approves Ava and gives her $1000 from the community treasury.
A 'no' denies this proposal.
author: 0x5ea400d06Afe7aebae54216aDfD7a4bF5f15F993
